short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension enhances phone number recognition on web pages.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: The extension manages phone communication on the web by making it communicate with a PBX desktop application. The extension is for specific group of people who owns that PBX desktop app. With this Extension, The owners of that PBX desktop app can easily identify and click on phone numbers on any website, allowing you to quickly and seamlessly initiate calls through that PBX desktop app. No more copying and pasting phone numbers.
